query: SELECT p.id, p.addressLine1, p.owner1Name, COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) as contact_count, COUNT(DISTINCT pt.id) as tag_count FROM properties p LEFT JOIN contacts c ON p.id = c.propertyId LEFT JOIN propertyTags pt ON p.id = pt.propertyId WHERE p.listName = 'Rolando' GROUP BY p.id LIMIT 5;
